  <original-body>@@@ ruby
class BankController &lt; ActionController::Base
  layout &quot;bank_standard&quot; # works
  layout :bank_standard  # FAILS
end
@@@

layout should accept both string and symbol as layout name.

In case symbol is specified as layout name then first a method call should be done to get layout name. However if no such method exists then apply the layout specified as symbol.</original-body>
